Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,小麵包  在的話就動一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:10.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,告訴我埃米莉可在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:12.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:19.20,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:21.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我在這裡  凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可  你在哪  你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:33.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒事吧  現在給你鬆開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:40.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:44.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你沒事真是太好了  現在馬上從這裡出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:46.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不是的  凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:47.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:50.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:55.20,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:57.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,愛德華
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:01.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可算沒讓我白等啊  凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我就知道你肯定會來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:07.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,畢竟你是為活人偶著想的影家人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:10.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你的目標一開始就是我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:18.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,到了早上你就會作為影宅的叛亂分子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:20.64,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,被帶到偉大的祖父大人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:24.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣的話我就能實現我的夙願  晉升進入三樓了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:29.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,來吧凱特  回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:33.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你在謀劃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:39.24,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你以為不說話還能逃得掉嗎  看來你還沒明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:44.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就算你不是叛亂分子  我也可以告發你違反規則
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,告發你穿著這身衣服出現在祖父大人這一棟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:52.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,, 凱特是來救被你拐走的埃米莉可…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你覺得這麼說會有人信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,身為大人的我和身為兒童的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:01.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,偉大的祖父大人會相信誰  答案很明顯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:07.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,一開始就已經分出勝負了  凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:14.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那麼慢慢等待偉大的祖父大人醒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:18.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你一定會受到嚴重的處罰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:21.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這說不定會是你的最後一杯紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:28.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,死心吧  你已經完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:04.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特  我現在去幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:39.63,Shadow house-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(397,517)\pos(1698,866.667)}為了影宅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在幾樓來著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊  好可怕  到一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:05:00.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩…我在找愛德華的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,叫我跟上去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我怎麼會上你的當…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:13.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,多了兩台推車  也就是說侵入者有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,保持警戒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:19.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我去向愛德華傳達  傑勒德搜查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他們應該是混入到無面人偶之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我…我去搜查侵入者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:31.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣你就幹不了壞事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,把他們全都當作叛亂分子交上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:24.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣我們肯定能去三樓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:33.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有在做好孩子嗎  看來終於放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:39.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,反抗影宅是愚蠢至極的行為  現在就算後悔也太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:44.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,最後的紅茶要涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:48.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  你這樣綁著喝不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:00.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:13.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不對  是喬恩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:16.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:17.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你是來幫我的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:21.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,當然  不過現在喬恩也需要幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這孩子是我們的同伴  趕緊跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩呢  找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:42.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒有  果然是去那邊幫凱特小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:47.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真是魯莽  希望他不會拖後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那露薏絲和露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她們看起來很睏的樣子  回房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,一個兩個都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:08:00.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,順利的話是時候該回來了吧  好擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對不起讓您擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:08.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不過我相信喬恩少爺  他肯定會帶著她們回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,恐怕到那個時候愛德華也會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那時才是帕利克少爺出場的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.97,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要怎麼阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不  這…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊  我沒什麼厲害的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:34.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可是  我覺得帕利克少爺想救伙伴的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是不會輸給任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:43.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克少爺最大的能力是勇敢美麗的心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是這樣的話  那也是受到了你的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,「露面」的時候  是你流著淚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,拜託喬恩和尚恩去救帕利克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:57.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,都是託你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:00.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,屋頂？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:16.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不會是要從這裡跳回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,相當遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:36.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,停止無謂的抵抗  你們已經完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:41.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因為你們反抗影宅  擅自侵入這棟樓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,先來兒童樓的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:48.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你們說的話誰會信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.20,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特  帶著埃米莉可飛起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩  你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,別管我  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在說什麼亂七八糟的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可  緊緊抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:15.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:27.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,放棄吧凱特  這不是以你的黑灰能力能過去的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:39.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在中途墜落死亡  是適合愚蠢叛亂者的結局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我怎麼會讓凱特死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:11:00.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,別小看喬恩我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,艾琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:15.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我怎麼會讓凱特死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣能飛到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:37.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,都怪我被抓住  給凱特小姐和喬恩少爺添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,現在就先別管那種事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可  不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:53.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,果然是出事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,能夠返回的路應該只有這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:58.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:16.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,來這邊  不要急慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:21.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:35.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,才不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:42.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,愛德華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:45.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特  喬恩怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:57.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩用黑灰能力幫我們飛了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是他可能因為反作用無法動彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.64,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,愛德華
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,盡給我找麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:25.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這裡是兒童棟  不會再讓你為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:29.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你們以為在和誰說話  搞清楚自己的立場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:35.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,想在影宅裡活下去  就捨棄掉無聊的同伴意識
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,死心吧  凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:45.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你們再這樣礙事我就把你們全都處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你這話是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你不是睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:08.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我轉變心意啦  把芭芭拉叫過來可是大功一件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣一來露薏絲就一定能進戴星組了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真是露薏絲的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,難以想像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:20.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,和祖父大人同住的棟裡的愛德華大人居然出現在兒童棟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:24.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,究竟是怎麼回事  還請麻煩您說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:27.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我作為兒童棟管理人 要對他們進行直接指導
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這大清早的要指導什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:34.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,剛才還說要全部處理掉  我倒不覺得這是指導
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:41.48,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就算你是管理人  擅自闖入兒童棟也是被禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:45.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我已經向三樓的各位匯報了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他們在走廊的盡頭等著您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這全都託您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:05.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,正因為有您「每天給我仔細巡邏」這般認真的指導
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:09.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們才能揭發如此嚴重的違規行為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.84,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:36.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這次真的十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,事到如今才乖乖道歉已經來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:44.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,愛德華  你被影宅放逐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您是說放逐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就算要給孩子們指導
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:54.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但你居然進到兒童棟裡拐走他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不要狡辯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:02.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你可是個在「露面」裡讓「臉」胡思亂想的問題人物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:07.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,總之這個宅邸不需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:11.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,需要的只有對偉大的祖父大人有用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:17.24,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,把愛德華放逐  剩下的兩人降級到一樓如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就這樣決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,愛德華
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:34.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你對孩子們大膽又獨特的指導  其實我很感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:38.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是這次你做得稍微過了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:48.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,包括愛德華在內的三人  給予嚴厲警告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:58.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,聽好了  下不為例
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:01.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是  今後我會繼續精進努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:17.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,處分是不是有點太便宜他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:24.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影宅似乎還有很多種可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,總歸是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是這樣一來離三樓更遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,愛德華  不要再擅自行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我還沒有放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,從這次寬容的決斷來看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我感受到了他對我的期待和愛護
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就算是為了回報這份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:57.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我也一定要把頑強又狡猾的反叛分子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,連同三樓的那群廢物們一起趕出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:05.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這全都是為了偉大的祖父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:23.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒有  只是能光明正大地從房間裡出來有點難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:27.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,而且能和凱特小姐並肩而行我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:33.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,說起來  喬恩少爺那之後怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:43.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,新人小姐  聚會至少應該早點到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:45.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  大家到的都很早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩  你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,其實那時我拚命抓住他回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:54.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,抓住愛德華騎的黑灰鴿子的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:57.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,多虧了那個奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,說起來露薏絲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:14.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,美麗的薔薇凱特  盛開的非洲菊露薏絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,說明會要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:19.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要學習宅邸裡正確的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:22.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:29.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐  話說那個到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那個  是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:36.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就是那個幫了我們的  小小的很可愛的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:39.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那個啊  真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:43.41,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那孩子為什麼會知道凱特能使用黑灰能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐  怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:48.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這是重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影族是優秀的貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:08.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,活人偶為侍奉影族而感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:20.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不可忘記要感謝影宅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:38.81,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,拭けば明日は  すすが積もる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:38.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,即使擦去黑灰明天也會積攢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:43.94,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,すすが積もれば  また拭ける
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:43.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,即使黑灰積攢也會再次擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:48.70,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,さあ  働きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:48.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,來工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:53.33,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,お役に立ちましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:53.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,派上用場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:58.38,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,余計なことは  考えない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:58.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,多餘的事情  不去考慮
